The property is located on the northern side of Lisbon Street approximately 450m west of Woodville Road. 

A prominent industrial location occupied by a variety of users of both a local and regional nature. Access to the M4 and the M5 Motorways is via Woodville Road and Henry Lawson Drive.

- 2,187sqm* building area
- Dangerous goods approved
- Internal clearance of up to 12.3m*
- Accessible via two (2) container height roller doors
- Large awning for all weather loading 
- Excellent truck access through a large hard stand forecourt
- Corporate office component fully carpeted & air conditioned.
- Fully sprinklered facility 
- Zoned IN1 General Industrial 

For further information or to arrange an inspection please contact either of the exclusive agents listed.

*approx.

CBRE is pleased to present 34-38 Lisbon Street, Fairfield East to the market for sale. The opportunity exists for a savvy investor or owner occupier to make use of the high building area and unlock its strong yield potential through multiple income streams.

34-38 Lisbon Street, Fairfield East boasts the following key attributes:

- Building area of 6,359sqm*
- Site area of 7,174sqm*
- 667sqm* basement storage or parking
- Internal warehouse clearances of up to 13m*
- Features an office/showroom, warehouse facility and freestanding office building
- Refurbished office and showroom currently utilised for kitchens and bathrooms
- Opportunity for vendor to leaseback part of the premises on a 5 year lease*
- Strong yield potential via multiple income streams
- Vacant possession also available
- Lounge suites, karaoke rooms and open room areas 
- Two substations on site 

For a copy of the information memorandum or to arrange an inspection, please contact the either of the listed agents.
